oracle.nosql.driver.ops

Class QueryRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.nosql.driver.ops.Request
      • oracle.nosql.driver.ops.QueryRequest

  • public class QueryRequest
extends Request
    A request that encapsulates a query. A query may be either a string query statement or a prepared query, which may include bind variables. A query request cannot have both a string statement and prepared query, but it must have one or the other.

    For performance reasons prepared queries are preferred for queries that may be reused. Prepared queries bypass compilation of the query. They also allow for parameterized queries using bind variables.

    See Also:
    NoSQLHandle.query(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.QueryRequest), NoSQLHandle.prepare(oracle.nosql.driver.ops.PrepareRequest)
